.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>UNDEAD</strong>: As <strong>Queen Freya</strong>, the Undead Queen, you will exhaust your friends and draw the life out of your foes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/1522812c06f5e46e2b87446ac2245b9d.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/1522812c06f5e46e2b87446ac2245b9d.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/1522812c06f5e46e2b87446ac2245b9d.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master Powerful Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fire Axe, Amulet of Fate, Shadow Shield and many others await you: collect treasure chests and fight monsters to uncover <strong>legendary weapons and artefacts</strong> your units can equip.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/81aff036ce90927c8ca30a471c4a51c9.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/81aff036ce90927c8ca30a471c4a51c9.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/81aff036ce90927c8ca30a471c4a51c9.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Channel Ancestral Magic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take advantage of your commander's <strong>unique powers</strong> to inspire your units, protect them from harm, or cause destruction on your enemies. Advance your level and <strong>unlock additional abilities</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2f25d8f79226cd09f2f6a01aa46dcc33.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2f25d8f79226cd09f2f6a01aa46dcc33.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2f25d8f79226cd09f2f6a01aa46dcc33.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat Nasty Monsters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The beautiful land of Liria is infested by monstrous creatures: some more common than others – like Goblins and Lizards – and some rare, like Balthazar, an ancient fearsome dragon. Defeat them and collect <strong>gold, loot, and XP points</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2064216c4bc451ac4531cc08b7983481.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2064216c4bc451ac4531cc08b7983481.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2064216c4bc451ac4531cc08b7983481.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unleash Epic Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Liria is a shape-shifting land: every session plays on a <strong>different map</strong>, making every scenario unique and challenging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/6c536037819f56bf93cf3c23ce2560c9.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/6c536037819f56bf93cf3c23ce2560c9.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/6c536037819f56bf93cf3c23ce2560c9.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
